{"tid":2318644,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔最愛的Tiffsir (個fd)","createTime":"2020-12-09T13:05:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T09:56:46.000Z","uid":382981,"like":17,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"bef9e49bf75482c181fea1da7b2c5804bc721fbf","tid":2318644,"uid":382981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T13:05:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CzWNOjJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCzWNOjJ.jpg&h=3ab17408&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\ntiff sir示意圖<br />\n話說連登仔最愛的Tiffsir 以前po呢個friend既時候<br />\n係遮撚住曬佢個樣 但係影撚住佢對波先PO<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F1KceZY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF1KceZY.jpg&h=243633c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n導致到好多咸濕佬走去follow佢個friend<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/89ece0s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F89ece0s.jpg&h=0f3a7b29&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n之後佢個friend就開始膨脹 以為自己好撚靚女所以啲人走去follow佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知有人喺tiff sir po佢真面目張相下面留言<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/khUztnz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkhUztnz.jpg&h=2c6ddcc8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nus5z2z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnus5z2z.jpg&h=63f665e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7L1VcPf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7L1VcPf.jpg&h=fd1348c9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n話佢其實勁樣衰 放返個樣出黎就唔會有人follow佢<br />\n條女比人講撚到中曬 然後發曬脾氣勁嬲咁話自己唔care <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實就崩口人忌崩口碗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba564a734ebaf5003431fb9dc391a81b72a8088c","tid":2318644,"uid":382981,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T13:08:59.000Z","msg":"膨脹師 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd10b9ad73e52002ffe84b08dbaa2c369a2cc8d2","tid":2318644,"uid":38904,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T13:13:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/UnlawfulHeartyChanticleer-size_restricted.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FUnlawfulHeartyChanticleer-size_restricted.gif&h=cf75d4f5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b87940c9efe6dbe9ea02ff3f3fc25b1020ec7016","tid":2318644,"uid":63842,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T13:20:47.000Z","msg":"成班垃圾毒撚係度盲目捧女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乜撚嘢Tiffsir識佢老味咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9136658602cc26f7022ab9a1773c7d75268d16ee","tid":2318644,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T13:28:01.000Z","msg":"求閪其啦"},{"pid":"36dac947234572a0ef861f9d3faa79b075df645a","tid":2318644,"uid":64809,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T13:36:39.000Z","msg":"關連登仔鳩事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無撚聊聊私鬥野"},{"pid":"15103ec5c3c4ca8e6699cd1b85acde7b8c1cfe92","tid":2318644,"uid":51307,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T13:39:37.000Z","msg":"樓主你做乜撚啫? 男人老狗成個8婆仔咁 柒撚到仆街"},{"pid":"8bdf9ddcf5bdb1c27244d9348e6ec671d58b41d6","tid":2318644,"uid":382981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9136658602cc26f7022ab9a1773c7d75268d16ee","tid":2318644,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"re